        "border": null,
        "shape": null
      },
      "text": "### Model Overview\n- Directed search model in the spirit of [[2010 - Guido Menzio, Shouyong Shi - Block recursive equilibria for stochastic models of search on the job|Menzio and Shi (2010)]]\n- Sources of heterogeneity:\n    - **Firms**: Different remote-work efficiencies.\n    - **Workers**: Different skill levels.\n- **Key Mechanisms**:\n    - Workers value the flexibility provided by remote work arrangements.\n    - High-skilled workers are more productive and better suited for remote work.\n    - Firms treat remote and on-site work as substitutable.",
